### Delete Post

This endpoint is used to delete a specific post by its ID.

#### Request

- Method: DELETE

- URL: `{{url_v1}}/posts/10`


#### Response

The response for this request can be described using the following JSON schema:

``` json
{
  "type": "object",
  "properties": {
    "status": {"type": "string"},
    "message": {"type": "string"},
    "post": {
      "type": "object",
      "properties": {
        "id": {"type": "integer"},
        "user_id": {"type": "integer"},
        "title": {"type": "string"},
        "slug": {"type": "string"},
        "content": {"type": "string"},
        "created_at": {"type": "string"},
        "updated_at": {"type": "string"},
        "deleted_at": {"type": "string"}
      }
    }
  }
}

 ```

